# Boki Loop Privacy Policy

Last updated: May 2026

Boki Loop respects your privacy.

## Information Collected

Boki Loop may collect limited information required for app functionality, including:

- Subscription status
- Anonymous purchase information
- Advertising-related identifiers
- Basic app usage data

Learning records and progress are stored locally on your device whenever possible.

## Third-Party Services

The app may use third-party services including:

- RevenueCat (subscription management)
- Google AdMob (advertising)

These services may collect information in accordance with their own privacy policies.

## Data Usage

Collected information is used only for:

- Providing app functionality
- Managing subscriptions
- Displaying advertisements
- Improving app stability

